OL,5, Drivers who kill could receive life    
OL,6, sentences as part of changes coming    
OL,7, into force this week.                  
OL,9,FJudges will be able to hand down life  
OL,10,Fsentences to dangerous drivers who kill
OL,11,Fand careless drivers who kill while    
OL,12,Funder the influence of drink or drugs. 
OL,14,FThe current penalty for each crime is a
OL,15,Fmaximum prison sentence of 14 years.   
OL,17,F"Those responsible will now face the   
OL,18,Fpossibility of life behind bars,"      
OL,19,FJustice Secretary Dominic Raab said.   
